videos.description: West Virginia's Lamount West hits a 3-pointer from the right corner to cut Long Beach State's lead to 9-6 in the first half.
videos.headline: West with a smooth corner three for WVU

videos.description: Sagaba Konate scores with a right-hand hook shot in the post as the Mountaineers extend the lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Konate lays in hook shot for WVU

videos.description: Sagaba Konate blocks shot for the Mountaineers and gains possession
videos.headline: Konate with a monster block for WVU

videos.description: Sagaba Konate denies Long Beach State' Barry Ogalue dunk attempt on the fast break.
videos.headline: Konate hosting a block party for WVU

videos.description: Bryan Alberts benefits from beautiful ball movement, which results in a 3-pointer in the first half.
videos.headline: Alberts' 3-ball pulls Long Beach State closer

videos.description: Chase Harler drains a 3-pointer off the bounce pass from Jevon Carter to extend the Mountaineers' lead.
videos.headline: Harler with 3-point stroke for West Virginia

videos.description: Chase Harler hits his fourth 3-pointer of the first half marking a career-high 12 points for WVU.
videos.headline: Harler continues hot shooting for WVU

videos.description: Gabe Levin dunks off the bullet pass from Edon Maxhuni to close the gap for Long Beach State.
videos.headline: Levin sneaks in a dunk for Long Beach State

videos.description: Lamont West swoops in to tip-in the missed shot to extend the Mountaineers' lead to 19.
videos.headline: WVU's West soars in for the tip
